#!/bin/bash
# 选择打包类型 echo "请选择打包类型：" echo "1. ad hoc" echo "2. appstore" echo "请先确认 打包配置文件是否正确:" echo "ad hoc: 文件路径 ios/exportOptions/exportOptions-adhoc.pliste" echo "appstore: 文件路径 ios/exportOptions/exportOptions-appstore.pliste" echo "---------------------------------------------------" read -p "请输入选项 (1 或 2): " distribution_type
# 根据用户输入确定分发类型和构建参数 case $distribution_type in 1) export DISTRIBUTION="adhoc" FLUTTER_BUILD_ARGS="--release --no-codesign" ;; 2) export DISTRIBUTION="appstore" FLUTTER_BUILD_ARGS="--release" ;; *) echo "无效的选项，脚本终止。" exit 1 ;; esac
# 执行 Flutter 构建 fvm flutter build ios $FLUTTER_BUILD_ARGS
# 检查构建是否成功 if [ $? -ne 0 ]; then echo "Flutter 构建失败，请检查错误。" exit 1 fi
# 获取项目名称 PROJECT_NAME=Runner
# 定义构建目录 BUILD_DIR="build/ios/archive"
# 创建输出目录（如果不存在） mkdir -p "$BUILD_DIR"
# 导航到 iOS 子目录 cd ios || { echo "无法进入 ios 目录"; exit 1; }
# 使用 xcodebuild 打包 IPA xcodebuild -workspace "$PROJECT_NAME.xcworkspace" \ -scheme "$PROJECT_NAME" \ -sdk iphoneos \ -configuration Release \ archive -archivePath "$BUILD_DIR/$PROJECT_NAME.xcarchive" \ EXPORT_OPTIONS_PLIST="exportOptions/exportOptions-$DISTRIBUTION.plist"
# 检查打包是否成功 if [ $? -ne 0 ]; then echo "IPA 打包失败，请检查错误。" exit 1 fi
echo "IPA 打包完成，文件位于: $BUILD_DIR/"
